duties_responsibilities.duty: Provide dental services to patients with the support of the dental team.
Use DentaPro software and Digital x-ray and Panorex units for diagnostics and treatment planning.
Adhere to yearly OSHA and HIPAA regulations, and Emergency Management training.
Work with a ratio of 1 hygienist, 1 hygiene assistant, and 2 dental assistants per provider.
Manage a patient base primarily consisting of ages 3-21, with up to 30% adult population, depending upon location.
Handle an office flow of an average of 10-12 operative patients and 20-25 hygiene patients.
Accept state insurance plans, PPO, and out-of-network payor mix.

education_certification.credential: DDS/DMD from a dental education program accredited by the Commission on Dental Accreditation
